  "info": {
    "name": "Management API Module Tests - Phase 10",
    "description": "Comprehensive tests for WeSign Management API covering:\n- Companies management (create, read, update, delete)\n- Users management (login, list, reset password, update)\n- Licenses management\n- System configuration\n\nNote: Management API uses separate authentication from User API.\nBase URL: {{managementBaseUrl}} = https://devtest.comda.co.il/managementapi/v3/\n\n**Controllers Covered:**\n- CompaniesController (7 endpoints)\n- UsersController (6 endpoints)\n- LicensesController\n- ConfigurationController\n- PaymentController\n- ProgramsController\n- ActiveDirectoryController\n- OTPController\n- ReportsController\n- LogsController",
